I3 cheatsheet


Resize mode: Mod + R – use arrow keys

Switch Tiling Mode: Mod + E (split) Mod + W (Tabbed) Mod  + S (Stacking)

Search For Programs: Mod + D (you can also search)

Move Windows – Mod + Shift + Arrow key of direction

Vertical Tiling – Mod + V

Open Terminal – Mod + Enter

Change which window has focus – Mod + Arrow Key

Switch workspace – Mod + Key Number

Switch workspace of a window – Mod + Shift + Number of workspace

Restart i3 – Mod + Shift + R

Log out/end session – Mod + Shift + E
